  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>新智元</span> <span>2025-10-31 12:46</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00bf5b44&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrEiayNicHUKiaC6FNaSUC0JnXSEia2bZicTicjDUXDx44kLcvDXAQiaAq7UkPw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505140601\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7Rr37ia28eOFJ7dsib9eOqdFdqskkv41VwGpWa5GGRTBqtku3NsVyc6hxsw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c9b6a519&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7Rr37ia28eOFJ7dsib9eOqdFdqskkv41VwGpWa5GGRTBqtku3NsVyc6hxsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding: 10px;font-size: 14px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;border-radius: 3px;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;word-break: break-all !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">GPT-5的惊艳之处，不只是写得好，还有超强的推理能力。近期的一个研究揭示了其中的秘密：通用智能体之所以聪明，不是因为参数更大，而是因为它们在脑子里长出了一张「世界模型」。而这张隐形的地图，也正在改变我们对AI的理解。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">GPT-5上线后，最让人震惊的不是它能写诗画画，而是它展现出的推理能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">网友惊呼：「感觉像是在和博士讨论问题」，媒体更是直言它的逻辑水平已经「堪比专家」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">为什么会出现这种「突然开窍」的效果？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">最新的一篇研究给出了答案：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">通用智能体之所以能推理，不靠死记硬背，而是因为它们在脑子里悄悄长出了一张「世界模型」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"107\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"366\" data-imgfileid=\"505140605\" data-ratio=\"0.18541033434650456\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1974\" data-width=\"1974\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0a1fd8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7Rriayvcewy3ucZUsaR8eKkepYHw1kmNQnbwNz8vrr62MUuS5egMoQREWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg4d4zx8w7y\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mg4d4zx0wgr\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">论文传送门：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2506.01622\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2506.01622</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;DBxSdl8KXoj025xUgdmcIrsZnOh&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;https://arxiv.org/pdf/2506.01622&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+w&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7114955059070337052&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;link-id&quot;,&quot;491e0a26-d643-4a1c-92dd-6904cffe38d4&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;fd7cd5ec-6713-4e24-b608-65deb396c9f5&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:37,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:5,&quot;end&quot;:37},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;VCYZdywqDohww7x0ADLcS8N7nxf&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">是模仿还是思考？学界吵了十年</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">什么是「世界模型」？简单来说，它就是AI脑子里的预测地图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于人类来说，我们的脑子里天生带有预测的功能：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">球在桌子边滚动→它可能会掉下去</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">开车的时候，看到红灯→如果不刹车可能出事故</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">两个人对话，其中一个人说「我饿了」→下一步很可能是找吃的</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那对于AI来说，是怎样的呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在过去的十几年里，学界一直在争吵——AI到底能不能只靠模仿（无模型学习），也能解决复杂任务？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「模仿派」认为，只要有足够多的数据+强大的算力，AI就能像条件反射一样给出正确答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在GPT-3.5时代，大部分AI的回答都像「背题库」，有时候蒙对，有时候完全错误。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与之相反的则是「思考派」。他们坚持如果没有世界模型，AI永远只是鹦鹉学舌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一旦问题需要多步逻辑，比如解数学习题、规划一个流程，纯模仿型AI就会掉链子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"443\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"606\" data-imgfileid=\"505140468\" data-ratio=\"0.788036410923277\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"769\" data-width=\"769\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=827c364f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrPzzMTicHbvsT3K3XAXcrOxCvjkicCyJhXedP6Ljtr7IhcH4hxKrvRv2w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近，有一研究给这些争论按下了终止键：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">只要一个智能体真的能完成多步、复杂的目标任务，它的策略里必然隐含了世界模型。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在学术框架里，「目标、策略、世界模型」曾经像一个缺角的三角形。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">已知世界模型和目标，可以推导出最优策略；已知策略和世界模型，可以反推出目标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"301\" data-backw=\"532\" data-height=\"301\" data-imgfileid=\"505140466\" data-ratio=\"0.5657894736842105\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"532\" data-width=\"532\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d34b2524&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7Rr80ZQcFrHT0v61DEKct4honMMPm9ibG6Mwr2kj0gMctqmSLE8j9iaIicnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mg4d5g1ibfs\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg4d5g1q15zq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图1 目标g、策略π、世界模型p之间的三角关系</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而现在最后一角也被补齐——只要知道智能体的策略和目标，就能恢复出它的世界模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个推导让「世界模型不可或缺」的结论更加稳固。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说，GPT-5之所以能展现出惊人的推理能力，是因为在训练过程中，它体内的「世界模型」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以说，没有世界模型，就没有真正的通用智能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">探究AI脑子里的地图</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仅有理论还不够，研究团队决定深入检查。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然说智能体一定会「长出」世界模型，那么我们能否在实验室里，把这张隐形的「地图」抓出来？</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">给AI搭建的「迷你世界」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了验证AI体内是否真的存在世界模型，研究团队设计了一个巧妙的实验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们搭建了一个虚拟世界，里面只有几个状态（X、Y），它们会按一定概率互相跳转。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后研究员将任务交给智能体，让它自己摸索。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后，研究人员尝试只根据智能体的行为，反推出它脑子里是不是已经学会了这些概率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"215\" data-backw=\"422\" data-height=\"215\" data-imgfileid=\"505140469\" data-ratio=\"0.509478672985782\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"422\" data-width=\"422\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8703c86f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrUpD3VbGGSINiaBcYibibD0nouHmMV9h4DqnYicxxSs2jLTKPWibqhpnXCMg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mg4d5x161m0q\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg4d5x1e8p7\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图2 智能体-环境系统示意图</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">任务越复杂，误差反而越小</span></strong></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">刚开始，智能体在简单目标里乱撞，恢复出来的世界模型差错很多，还有一堆错误。</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可当任务变得复杂（比如要先到X，再转到Y），情况就完全不同：它会自动搭建出更精细的「转移概率表」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着任务深度增加，误差迅速下降。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"238\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"426\" data-imgfileid=\"505140465\" data-ratio=\"0.4234592445328032\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1006\" data-width=\"1006\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b74b9ba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrXojiaibRXJxIfB42GRm6aS4gHgG08viaVib24VTjGWQP5ibnyW13OO4FiafA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mg4d61qu1cp\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg4d61r2f8q\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图3 任务复杂度vs世界模型误差曲线</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论是训练样本还是任务深度，结果都一边倒——任务越复杂，世界模型越准确。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验员还尝试了更复杂的目标组合：智能体需要在不同状态之间来回跳转，才能完成目标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"195\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"212\" data-imgfileid=\"505140467\" data-ratio=\"0.3464052287581699\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"612\" data-width=\"612\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cfdc117f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrPJ4NiavG6EEIByQjgbb7j29KWAicrKdtu74Q48mzafRvhYVepuCPOXzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mg4d67yx1m6o\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg4d67z51ifs\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图4 复合目标实验示意图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果依旧成立。即使任务被拆解得更复杂，它体内的世界模型依然能被稳定恢复出来。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">没有世界地图，就没有真正的智能</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数学推理也印证了这一点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验表明，只要一个智能体在复杂任务里不会频繁犯低级错误，始终能保持有限的「后悔值」，它的策略中就必然已经包含了环境的转移规律。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说——世界模型不是AI的点缀，而是它进化的必需品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能体越强，心里的「小九九」就越多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就是为什么GPT-5会让人觉得「突然会推理了」，其实是它体内越来越清晰的世界模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一张地图带来的希望与隐忧</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验告诉我们：只要AI能完成复杂任务，它的脑子里就一定有一个「世界地图」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这也解释了近来最热门的现象——所谓的「涌现能力」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究表示，这并不是魔法，而是世界模型在任务中逐渐清晰的自然结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们以为GPT-5突然会推理，其实是因为它体内的世界模型在任务中逐渐清晰，于是能力自然显现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这让人类看到了希望：如果世界模型真的存在，我们或许有机会把它抽离出来，借此理解AI的内心剧场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来，当它越来越强时，这可能成为破解黑箱、提升安全性的关键。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这也埋下了隐忧的种子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真实世界远比实验室复杂，AI学到的地图也许是模糊不完整的，甚至与人类理解不一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可能它觉得安全，而我们觉得危险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对研究者来说，这也是一个转机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然世界模型必然存在，那么我们或许能在未来把它抽取出来，用来解释和验证AI的行为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，破解「黑箱」不再只是愿景，而可能有了真正的理论支撑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，GPT-5带来的震惊不只是「它会推理」，更深层的意义在于：AI已经能在脑海里搭建自己的世界地图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而这张地图，既可能是通向智慧的通行证，也可能是未来不确定性的源头。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.01622\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.01622</a></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"122\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505133683\" data-ratio=\"0.2111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f15ce8a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1y6B5OM79TFzpkceWtUkI6LEwv0uYicSoM5Q3I3kDNJhxWdL3tQvbOpU3Ty7icBqnDDNd4CCu4ibiaHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"355\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505123771\" data-ratio=\"0.6138888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d635e771&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYSSrl5MkKQnew6tJZbEl11vWoXJSl8KN49xb9tqpzib1NficyeTibm3pzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2652640662\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=0efb4ecf&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI3MTA0MTk1MA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2652640662%26idx%3D3%26sn%3Db3beb36d2db63486ec7561ac814a5c19\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepMind 论文揭示 GPT-5 等通用智能体的推理能力源于其内部构建的“世界模型”，而非单纯模仿。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepMind 论文揭示 GPT-5 等通用智能体的推理能力源于其内部构建的“世界模型”，而非单纯模仿。",
  "summary": "文章围绕 DeepMind 一篇最新研究，探讨了 GPT-5 等大型语言模型展现出惊人推理能力的原因。该研究终结了学界长达十年的“模仿还是思考”之争，指出通用智能体之所以能进行多步复杂推理，是因为它们在训练过程中内隐地构建了“世界模型”，即像人类大脑中的预测地图一样，对环境转移规律的内在理解。文章通过实验验证了这一观点，发现在 AI 完成复杂任务时，其内部世界模型会变得更加精确。这一发现不仅解释了 AI 的“涌现能力”，也为理解 AI 的内部机制和提升其安全性提供了新的方向，同时也暗示了未来 AI 发展中可能存在的隐忧。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "通用智能体的推理能力源于内部构建的“世界模型”",
      "explanation": "DeepMind 研究表明，AI 并非靠死记硬背，而是在处理复杂任务时，内隐地学习并构建了对环境的预测地图，这是其展现推理能力的关键。"
    },
    {
      "point": "世界模型是 AI 完成复杂多步任务的必然产物",
      "explanation": "实验证明，当 AI 处理的任务越复杂，其内部恢复出的世界模型就越准确，这表明世界模型是 AI 实现真正智能的必需品。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“涌现能力”是世界模型逐渐清晰的自然结果",
      "explanation": "AI 突然展现出的推理等“涌现能力”，并非魔法，而是其内部世界模型在任务驱动下逐渐清晰化和完善的自然体现。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "通用智能体之所以能推理，不靠死记硬背，而是因为它们在脑子里悄悄长出了一张「世界模型」。",
    "只要一个智能体真的能完成多步、复杂的目标任务，它的策略里必然隐含了世界模型。",
    "没有世界模型，就没有真正的通用智能。",
    "世界模型不是 AI 的点缀，而是它进化的必需品。",
    "AI 已经能在脑海里搭建自己的世界地图。而这张地图，既可能是通向智慧的通行证，也可能是未来不确定性的源头。"
  ],
